dct_title_s: Map of Minnesota : school and other state lands, for sale during 1912
dct_description_sm: Cartographic Details: Scale not given. "Tracts for sale in 1912, shown in red." Shows state lands for sale in Koochiching, Beltrami, Cass, Itasca, St. Louis, Aitkin and Roseau counties. Dimensions: 69 x 85 centimeters
